features.text:
Ancient Future Gallery is showing art that celebrates cultural heritage in the future. showing artist from different cultures for something bigger than ourselves. It represents our history and our identity; our bond to the past, to our present, and the future.
Time can erase empires and kingdoms. History on the other hand written by the victor often distort  and makes the loser unable to tell their side of the story. One of the most iconic ways to study cultures of the world is through their art. Most of these art pieces are getting lost everyday. How can these great untold stories be heard? The Ancient Future Gallery is using the opportunity presented to the world with reference to blockchain technology to hold and display art that celebrates cultural heritage of artists from diverse cultures. The ripple effect is enormous, because on the blockchain you are assured of an eternal record keeping of data in our case digital art. This move by the Ancient Future Gallery is here to help artists capture and represent their history and preserve their cultural heritage, for others and their future generations to learn from the past, understand today and plan for the future. This is what the Ancient Future Gallery stands for. You are welcome to our metaverse.
